***LIVE AT 11PM ET*** MILO at Berkeley on Cultural Appropriation by Breitbart Tech 1 Feb 2017 0
In the final stop on his groundbreaking “Dangerous Faggot Tour,” which has enraged leftists and enthused political rebels all across America, MILO will deliver a speech at UC Berkeley, birthplace of the 1960s Free Speech Movement. MILO will be speaking about “cultural appropriation,” the bizarre new idea from social justice warriors that adopting or using the elements of a culture that is not one’s own – like a native american headdress, a sombrero, or dreadlocks – is somehow racist.
MILO’s speech will begin at 8pm Pacific Time, or 11pm Eastern Time.
